}}</ref>液氫的溫度極低，所以和其他低溫液體一樣有一定的危險性，比如會引致[[凍傷|凍傷]]。<ref>{{cite web| title=Liquid Hydrogen MSDS| publisher=Praxair, Inc.| date=September 2004| url=http://www.hydrogenandfuelcellsafety.info/resources/mdss/Praxair-LH2.pdf| format=PDF| accessdate=2008-04-16| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080527233910/http://www.hydrogenandfuelcellsafety.info/resources/mdss/Praxair-LH2.pdf| archivedate=2008-05-27}}</ref>氫氣可以溶解在多種金屬之中，除了可能的洩漏以外，氫氣還會造成金屬的[[氫脆|氫脆]]現象，<ref>{{cite journal| title='Bugs' and hydrogen embrittlement| journal=Science News| volume=128| issue=3| page=41| location=Washington, D.C.| date=1985-07-20|doi=10.2307/3970088| jstor=3970088}}</ref>引致材料爆裂。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.twi.co.uk/content/oilgas_casedown29.html|title=Union Oil Amine Absorber Tower|last=Hayes|first=B.|publisher=TWI|accessdate=2010-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081120215355/http://www.twi.co.uk/content/oilgas_casedown29.html|archive-date=2008-11-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>洩漏到空氣中的氫氣無色無味，且可以自燃，產生高溫但几乎不可见的火焰，因此有意外灼傷的可能性。<ref name=Cunn88>{{cite book|last1=Walker|first1=James L.|last2=Waltrip|first2=John S.|last3=Zanker|first3=Adam|editor1=John J. McKetta|editor2=William Aaron Cunningham|title=Lactic acid to magnesium supply-demand relationships|date=1988|publisher=Dekker|location=New York|isbn=082472478X|page=186|url=https://books.google.com.au/books?id=8erDL_DnsgAC&pg=PA186|accessdate=2015-05-20|work=Encyclopedia of Chemical Processing and Design|volume=28|archive-date=2015-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150522125721/https://books.google.com.au/books?id=8erDL_DnsgAC&pg=PA186|dead-url=no}}</ref>

氫的許多性質都受到了其自旋異構體（正氫和仲氫）比例的影響。不少數據所描述的是處於平衡態的氫氣，但氫氣有時需要幾天乃至幾週的時間才會達致平衡，所以它的安全數據可能和現實中的氫氣有所差別。另外，容器的形狀，也會大大影響氫氣的爆炸臨界溫度和壓力。<ref name=NASAH2/>

